entries.femaleVariant: Had a few adventures lately.
So, betcha can't guess who the FIA's newest, super secret, super badass agent is.
You yankin' my chain, V? Hold up, this isn't about my, er, tax sitch, is it?
Rescued the president of the NUSA, plain and simple.
'Member the Space Force One crash? In Dogtown? Rosalind Myers was on board – me an' this other FIA agent rescused 'er.
Pretty much how it happened, yeah. Long story short, Myers is safe now, I've made some new chooms…
FIA could save my life.
Tell you another time.
If all goes well, FIA'll help me out. Y'know, they got th emeans to patch up the ol' brain – fix me up for good.
Tell you about it some other time, Ker.
Ahhhh, so that's how the sneaky fuckers roped you in.
Lookin' forward to it.
You know, get a tinglin' in my ballsack when someone lies to me? Don't feel that now. So what – you were in Dogtown, plane flew right over your head?
Got a heap o' new problems too, I bet. Hey, NUSA prez versus one of the greatest rockerboys ever – who'd you put eddies on?
Tough one, that. You've got global reach, fans in the thousands, aaaand she's got a nuclear arsenal.
You think I'm bein' used. And I'm lettin' it happen.
Hey, if I was you, I'd try everythin' available. So I dig it. Just be careful with 'em. "A" in FIA stands for "assholes," y'know.
